odase

Class ModelWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.ModelWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HedwigModel, Model, ModelReadOnly, ModelUpdate, SwrlModel, ValidatableModel

    public class ModelWrapper
extends Object
implements Model
    This class provides a wrapper around a Model. It is useful when you want to intercept methods in the model or provide extra features without subclassing the model class. Subclassing may not be an option if all you have is a factory-generated reference to the model whose methods you want to intercept.
